                        <provenance>The name of the original owner has regularly been erased and substituted, first by
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14507QalaHaymanot">Qāla hāymānot</persName></foreign>.
                            This name was in turn occasionally blotted out or erased and substituted by 
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14510BakwraWald">Bakʷra Wald</persName></foreign>
                            (e.g. on <locus target="#25vc #28va #33vc"/>).
                            Either the first or the second of these names were later blotted out or erased and substituted by
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14508Azaryas">ʾAzāryās</persName></foreign> or, occasionally,
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14509WaldaEsrael">Walda ʾƎsrāʾel</persName></foreign>
                            (e.g. on <locus target="#21vc #25vc"/>) or 
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14512Pistis">Ṗisṭis</persName></foreign>
                            (e.g. on <locus target="#34vb #37vb"/>).
                            On <locus target="#132vc"/>, the original name has been substituted by
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14513WalattaYohannes">Walatta Yoḥannəs</persName></foreign>,
                            which in turn was substituted by 
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14514NegestMaryam">Nəgəśt Māryām</persName></foreign>.
                            <bibl><ptr target="bm:Zettersteen1899Upsala"/><citedRange unit="page">515–518</citedRange></bibl> and
                            <bibl><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><citedRange unit="page">43–45</citedRange></bibl>
                            only mention the two layers of ownership: 
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14507QalaHaymanot">Qāla hāymānot</persName></foreign>
                            followed by <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14508Azaryas">ʾAzāryās</persName></foreign> and
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr"><persName ref="PRS14509WaldaEsrael">Walda ʾƎsrāʾel</persName></foreign>.
                        </provenance>
